snippet.title: Teaser to game "Wealth Project", coming soon..
snippet.description:
We are happy to announce that the release of the teaser to our educational game "Wealth Project" is out now! 

The game purpose is to change understanding of financial growth and enrich everybody, who strive for  financial freedom.  

"Wealth Project" game  is especially beneficial for the next generation, providing essential financial knowledge that isn't typically taught in schools. Learning about finance through gameplay makes the process much more fun and enjoyable!


Check out our game on Steam, and don't forget to add it to your Wishlist to stay updated on its release date.. 👾
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2333740/Wealth_Project/  

We are exited to see you try our game! ✨

Follow us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61558131976721
